think about
maybe what he might

14:29.202 --> 14:30.602
want you to say,
and then say that.

14:31.604 --> 14:33.071
{CHUCKLES}

14:33.073 --> 14:34.038
You're gonna be great.

14:47.586 --> 14:49.220
Thank you.

