Because the "K"
looks different.

15:54.287 --> 15:57.956
That's wonderful!
Oh, Wade, I'd love to
hear one of your songs.

15:59.124 --> 16:00.425
Ah, no.

16:00.427 --> 16:03.428
Mom, no, he just got here.
So don't...

16:03.430 --> 16:06.597
