And I say "kan" with a "K."

16:06.599 --> 16:08.299
{ALL LAUGH}

16:08.301 --> 16:09.567
Good one,
Mr. Peeples.

16:09.569 --> 16:11.336
Judge.

16:11.338 --> 16:13.137
