Impress us.

16:13.139 --> 16:14.005
{CHUCKLING}

16:15.407 --> 16:16.607
All right. Okay.

16:18.711 --> 16:21.579
This is a little something.
It's not my best,

16:23.549 --> 16:26.718
but it's a song
about teaching kids
to express themselves

16:26.720 --> 16:29.587
rather than urinate on stuff.

16:31.256 --> 16:32.657
Sounds timeless.

