Hey, what does that mean?

24:36.209 --> 24:38.209
It's a thing that we've done
since we were kids.

24:38.211 --> 24:39.910
Dad says,
"Run, chickens, run,"

24:39.912 --> 24:40.978
and the first one
to get home wins.

24:40.980 --> 24:42.746
Wins what?

24:42.748 --> 24:45.483
Just wins, babe.
That's the point with Dad.

24:45.485 --> 24:47.618
You should try to win.

24:47.620 --> 24:48.652
Daddy likes a winner?

24:48.654 --> 24:50.588
Go! Go!

24:50.590 --> 24:51.622
Do it!
I'm gone!

24:51.624 --> 24:52.623
Get him, babe!

24:54.226 --> 24:55.693
Watch out.
See y'all!

24:55.695 --> 24:57.061
Trying to impress Virgil.

24:57.063 --> 24:58.229
Aren't we all?

24:59.231 --> 25:00.064
{HONKING HORN}

25:03.635 --> 25:05.135
Go, go, go, babe!

25:08.573 --> 25:10.107
I'll get you now,
Mr. Peeples!

25:11.276 --> 25:12.643
{GROWLS}

25:14.546 --> 25:15.212
{PANTING}

25:17.682 --> 25:18.883
Hey, hey, yeah.

25:22.287 --> 25:23.120
{GROANS}
{THUNDER RUMBLING}

25:44.209 --> 25:45.309
Do you have a mop?

25:59.057 --> 26:00.724
Here's your tea.

26:00.726 --> 26:02.893
Thank you.
You're welcome.

26:02.895 --> 26:06.196
Did I really
cause the rain?

26:06.198 --> 26:07.731
Don't worry about it.
It's clearing up.

26:11.703 --> 26:12.603
Mmm.

26:14.172 --> 26:16.073
Oh, wow.
That's quite a headpiece.

26:16.075 --> 26:17.675
Let me ask you,
did you get that directly

26:17.677 --> 26:19.043
from outer space
or was there a middle man?

26:19.045 --> 26:21.679
A Martian broker?
{CHUCKLES}

26:21.681 --> 26:25.849
Come on, now. It was the '70s.
Bowie was to blame
for those outfits.

26:25.851 --> 26:28.018
Ah, Bowie, okay.

26:28.020 --> 26:28.953
Oh.

26:30.855 --> 26:32.790
Are you Lady Divine?

26:32.792 --> 26:35.259
You heard of me?
As young as you are?

26:35.261 --> 26:39.597
<i>Heard of you? So Gone Sucka
was my mama's break-up anthem.</i>

26:39.599 --> 26:41.832
Every time I heard that,
I knew somebody
was getting the ax.

26:41.834 --> 26:43.734
Stop. I love that.

26:43.736 --> 26:45.636
{BOTH CHUCKLE}

26:45.638 --> 26:48.606
Oh. And y'all...
You ladies were...

26:48.608 --> 26:49.773
What?

26:49.775 --> 26:50.874
Y'all were kind of nasty.

26:50.876 --> 26:52.309
No.

26:52.311 --> 26:55.245
<i>That song Turn You On, shoot.</i>

26:55.247 --> 26:58.949
<i>¶¶ Ooh ahh¶¶
¶¶   I'm gonna give you some!¶¶</i>

