27:12.063 --> 27:16.000
I don't know. It was
a million years ago.

27:16.002 --> 27:19.269
But it's such a big
part of who you are.

27:19.271 --> 27:22.206
Yeah.
Well, I guess you're right.

27:22.208 --> 27:24.642
You know,
I never would have guessed

27:24.644 --> 27:26.877
that my first
album was my last,

27:26.879 --> 27:28.846
because singing
was everything to me.

27:28.848 --> 27:31.982
But with the kids
and Virgil's career,

27:31.984 --> 27:34.318
it just became
too much to balance,
you know?

27:35.887 --> 27:37.921
But that's cool.
That's life.

27:40.992 --> 27:44.194
Oh, my God.
Is this Virgil?

27:44.196 --> 27:46.830
DAPHNE: With his fine self.
{CHUCKLES}

