He put himself
through law school
playing clubs.

27:51.904 --> 27:54.104
No, like Ashford & Simpson?

27:54.106 --> 27:55.706
Look here.
Look at my little Gracie.

27:57.008 --> 27:59.309
She looks different.

27:59.311 --> 28:01.879
Yeah. That was before
she got the boobies.

28:01.881 --> 28:03.180
She what?

28:03.182 --> 28:04.214
You know.

28:08.920 --> 28:10.020
You didn't know?

28:13.024 --> 28:16.393
Oh, baby, now I don't mean
to get up in your business,

28:16.395 --> 28:18.829
but how did you not know?

28:20.065 --> 28:22.232
I mean, you don't...
She doesn't...

28:22.234 --> 28:23.834
Yes, yes,
I just... I don't...

28:26.037 --> 28:27.237
I don't know
how I missed that.

28:27.239 --> 28:29.840
Yeah. I don't either.

28:32.911 --> 28:36.880
You know,
all the women in my family
are quite buxom.

28:36.882 --> 28:40.317
And Gloria over there,
she got the family heirlooms,
so to speak,

28:40.319 --> 28:43.487
and all the male attention
when they were growing up.

28:43.489 --> 28:46.957
Poor Grace.
Her being so competitive,
she couldn't accept it.

28:48.193 --> 28:50.294
So a couple of
summers ago...

28:50.296 --> 28:52.429
Okay, you two. Dinner's ready.

28:55.366 --> 28:56.800
What?

28:56.802 --> 28:57.434
Nothing.

28:59.971 --> 29:01.772
Mom, you look
great in that blouse.

29:01.774 --> 29:03.373
Thanks, honey. {CHUCKLES}

29:10.115 --> 29:13.050
GRACE: From where?

29:13.052 --> 29:14.918
I'm sorry, Wade.
I forgot to set
a place for you.

29:14.920 --> 29:15.786
WADE: Thank you.

29:19.357 --> 29:20.390
GLORIA: Everything
seems so pretty.

29:22.393 --> 29:25.529
Enjoying the spread
set before you, Wade?

29:25.531 --> 29:29.399
Wade, you are in for
a treat. Virgil has made
his lobster risotto.

29:29.401 --> 29:30.834
GRACE: Love
Daddy's lobster risotto.

29:30.836 --> 29:32.302
GLORIA: Daddy's best dish.

29:32.304 --> 29:34.271
You're a chef, huh?
It looks incredible.

29:34.273 --> 29:36.340
Thank you.

29:36.342 --> 29:40.010
I took up cooking and a couple
of other hobbies
